      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MARITIME EXPRESS (1) went close at Gundagai over 1400m before a short-head defeat here over 1200m. Maps for a soft run and winning rider Heywood stays aboard. Will get every chance to go one better. ROYALTOWN (4) did a big job winning his Maiden here on debut. Will have taken fitness and learning and the promising galloper looks capable of going back-to-back. GROUP CHAT (7) was expected to win here third-up but didn't have the best of it. The longer sprint will suit and she deserves another chance. BULLA VINAKA (5) has been knocking on the door and tumbles in weight at this level. Has an inside gate and keep him onside.",
